title: ONET GALLERY 3D
description: Ready for some classic Onet Connect fun in a new and realxing 3D look? Then get ready for Onet Gallery 3D! No time pressure and stress at all, just pure relaxing Onet fun. Connect blocks of the same color with each other to make them disappear. But keep and eye out for other blocks blocking the way, it's important to solve the boards in the right order and strategy. After successfully solving the board, you can watch the impressive figures in your personal gallery. Sounds great? Then waste no time and complete your awesome Onet Gallery!
